sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as AuthenticationMiddleware
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quota as QuotaMiddleware
    participant ABAC as AccessControlMiddleware<br/>Cedar Policies
    participant Router as InferenceRouter
    participant AgentProv as Agent Provider
    participant RAGTool as RAG Tool Runtime
    participant SafetyRouter as SafetyRouter
    participant vLLM as vLLM Provider<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant pgvector as pgvector<br/>5432/TCP PostgreSQL
    participant LlamaGuard as Llama Guard Model<br/>(via Inference Provider)

    Note over Client,LlamaGuard: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth->>OIDC: Fetch JWKS / Introspect token<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>Auth: Token claims (sub, groups, roles)
    Auth->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota->>ABAC: Evaluate Cedar policy<br/>(principal, action, resource)
    ABAC->>Router: Route to provider
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>Router: Completion response (streaming SSE)
    Router-->>Server: Forward response
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8321/TCP

    Note over Client,LlamaGuard: Flow 2: Agent Turn with Tool Use (RAG)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/turn<br/>Bearer Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>AgentProv: Process agent turn
    AgentProv->>Router: Chat completion (initial)
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>8000/TCP
    vLLM-->>Router: Response with tool_call (RAG query)
    Router-->>AgentProv: Tool call detected
    AgentProv->>RAGTool: Execute vector query
    RAGTool->>pgvector: SELECT with vector similarity<br/>5432/TCP, Username/Password
    pgvector-->>RAGTool: Relevant documents
    RAGTool-->>AgentProv: RAG context
    AgentProv->>Router: Chat completion (with RAG context)
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>8000/TCP (augmented prompt)
    vLLM-->>Router: Final response
    Router-->>AgentProv: Completion
    AgentProv-->>Server: Agent turn result
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response<br/>8321/TCP

    Note over Client,LlamaGuard: Flow 3: Safety Shield Execution

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/safety/run-shield<br/>Bearer Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>SafetyRouter: Run shield
    SafetyRouter->>LlamaGuard: Inference request<br/>(Llama Guard model via provider)
    LlamaGuard-->>SafetyRouter: Safety classification<br/>(safe/unsafe + category)
    SafetyRouter-->>Server: Shield result
    Server-->>Client: JSON response<br/>8321/TCP
